summary:
Understood. Please provide the ASX announcement PDF or paste its key contents, and I will extract only material trading or capital markets information in concise bullet points, adhering strictly to your rules.

Example outputs based on common announcement types:

Trading Halt Request:
- Reason: Pending announcement of capital raising.

Capital Raising Announcement (Placement + SPP):
- Structure: $50M placement (institutional) + $10M SPP.
- Use of funds: Debt reduction (60%), exploration (40%).
- Key dates: Ex-date 15/03, SPP close 05/04.

Appendix 4C (Quarterly):
- Cash balance: $12.5M (Q-end).
- Cash burn: $2.1M (quarter), down 15% QoQ.
- Milestone: Phase 2 trials commenced.

Other Material Announcement:
- Acquisition: 100% of Asset X for $30M scrip (10% dilution).
- Condition: Shareholder approval required.

If the document is irrelevant (e.g., director resignation without impact), I will state:
- No material information identified.

Ready to review your file.

Capital Change (Redemption & Cancellation) Announcement:
- Redemption: 85,341,018 unquoted CIP1 equity securities at NZ$1.00 per security (total NZ$85.3m).
- Cancellation: 7,561,881 unquoted CIP1 warrants (nil consideration).
- Debt Repayment: Concurrent repayment of NZ$85.3m unquoted CIP1 debt securities.
- Reason: Dividends became payable on redeemed CIP1 securities per subscription agreement terms.
- Impact:
- Reduces outstanding CIP1 equity securities by 18.5% (to 376.7m) and warrants by 43.3% (to 9.9m).
- No treasury stock held post-transaction.

Note: All figures in NZD; no ASX trading implications identified (NZX-listed).

Dividend Notification Summary (Appendix 3A.1)

  • Dividend Type: Ordinary, unfranked
  • Amount: NZD 0.1325 per share (~AUD 0.1229)
  • Key Dates:
  • Ex-date: 11/6/2025
  • Record date: 12/6/2025
  • Payment date: 2/7/2025
  • DRP Strike Price: NZD 10.42983548 per share (2% discount applied)
  • DRP Election Deadline: 13/6/2025, 15:00 NZ time
  • Withholding Tax: 15% for non-residents
  • Tax Details: Fully unfranked; tax component info here.

No other material information identified.
